Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: US foreign policy unclear
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bt68
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 16 Jul 1978
President Carter sends out unclear messages on foreign policy. Ambassador Young's gaffe over political prisoners. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less